<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`Material`<sp/>-<sp/>Shader<sp/>+<sp/>default<sp/>MaterialProperties</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`MaterialProperties`<sp/>-<sp/>Immutable<sp/>value<sp/>object<sp/>(baseColor,<sp/>roughness,<sp/>etc.)</highlight></codeline>
