<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::make_shared&lt;MaterialProperties&gt;(materialProps));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>4.<sp/>Input<sp/>System</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Unified<sp/>input<sp/>handling<sp/>for<sp/>keyboard,<sp/>mouse,<sp/>and<sp/>gamepad.</highlight></codeline>
